Changing between collections (Groups)

You can skip this section if you are not assigned more than one collection/permission group.
1. Right click anywhere in the Command Center and click on Options
2. Click the "Security" tab
3. Click the "Active Group" dropdown to select the collection you want to switch to

The choices available to you will depend on what permissions you have been assigned to.

4. Click "Earth Sciences Collections Manager"

In this example, we are switching from "Anthropology Collections Manager" to "Earth Sciences Collection Manager".

5. Click "OK"

You should be now logged in as "Earth Sciences Collection Manager".
